37:37.272 --> 37:37.733
Oh, no.

37:37.753 --> 37:38.634
He bought it all.

37:38.794 --> 37:47.410
And as a matter of fact, there are huge discrepancies between how many tens or hundreds of thousands of items

37:47.879 --> 37:48.921
It included.

37:48.941 --> 37:53.349
